;;; {"type":"html","content":"<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" alt=\"\" />","value":"#object[java.awt.image.BufferedImage 0x597427be \"BufferedImage@597427be: type = 10 ColorModel: #pixelBits = 8 numComponents = 1 color space = java.awt.color.ICC_ColorSpace@126e9c64 transparency = 1 has alpha = false isAlphaPre = false ByteInterleavedRaster: width = 30 height = 30 #numDataElements 1 dataOff[0] = 0\"]"}
